    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been meticulously maintained to showroom standards. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with no scratches or dents, and the interior remains pristine, smelling fresh with no signs of wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it performs flawlessly; the engine runs quietly and smoothly, the transmission shifts perfectly, and there are absolutely no leaks or underlying issues. This is a rare find for a buyer looking for a car that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
